import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Router, Routes } from "react-router-dom"
import ToDo from './components/ToDo'
import Navbar from './components/Navbar'

const App = () => {
  return (
      <BrowserRouter>
        <Routes>
          <Route path="/todo" element={<ToDo/>}/>
        </Routes>
      </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
